Whatsapp - Facebook-messenger Readme

Design a Chat Application

Functional Requirements
    -> One-to-One Chat
    -> Group Chat
    -> Text/Images/Videos/Documents
    -> Read Receipt
        Single Tick - when message is sent
        Double Tick - when message is delivered to user
        Blue Tick - When person sees the message
    -> Last Seen


Non-Functional Requirements

    -> Low Latency
    -> High Availability
    -> No Lag
    -> Scale
        2 Billion Users
        Out of which 1.6 Billion Monthly access
        65 Billion Messages/Day
